Subject: Cososys DLP Server not booting up.
Description:
/dv/sda4 contains a file system with errors,check forced.
Inodes that were part of a corrupted orphan linked list found.

/dev/sda4: UNEXPECTED INCONSISTENCY; RUN FSCK MANUALLY.

fsck exited with status code 4
The root filesystem on /dev/sda4 requires a manual fsck

BusyBox v1.27.2 (Ubuntu 1:1.27.2-ubuntu3.4) built-in shell (ash)
What_We_Know__c: Client is not able to load up the epp server on their Ubuntu 18.04 server as they keep getting the fsck exited with status code 4 error.
Next_Steps__c: Need to gather more details about this internally and will have to get back to the client.
Solution_Comment__c:
Closing ticket as resolved.
Issue sorted after running e2fsck -f /dev/sda4
